text:
Corsair Abidjan service canceled from late-October 2015   
Sep 23, 2015 eTN   
Beginning the winter of 2015/2016, Corsair is canceling service to Cote d’Ivoire, as the airline closed its reservation for the Paris Orly – Abidjan route. The airline originally planned to operate three weekly flights with A330, on/after October 25, 2015. 
Previously planned schedule as follow. SS984 ORY1515 – 2045ABJ 330 257 SS985 ABJ2250 – 0620+1ORY 330 257
